::Slayer::

Slayer sees the two missiles heading for Thyphon, relieved that 
Ignatius was at least helping out.

"This might get bumpy," Slayer says, picking out a new course and 
flying off. He gains speed, heading toward the Cybertronian Fire.

"This might get pathetic, so ignore anything I say to anyone else," 
he tells Ignatius.
